<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for Craftal Web Designs. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our small business web design website." />
    <title>Privacy Policy - Craftal Web Design Agency</title>
    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/src/images/favicon.ico" />
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/png"
      sizes="16x16"
      href="/src/images/favicon-16x16.png"
    />
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/png"
      sizes="32x32"
      href="/src/images/favicon-32x32.png"
    />
    <link
      rel="apple-touch-icon"
      sizes="180x180"
      href="/src/images/apple-touch-icon.png"
    />

    <!-- Preload critical fonts -->
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/src/fonts/Satoshi-Regular.otf"
      as="font"
      type="font/otf"
      crossorigin
    />
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/src/fonts/Satoshi-Medium.otf"
      as="font"
      type="font/otf"
      crossorigin
    />
    <link
      rel="preload"
      href="/src/fonts/Satoshi-Bold.otf"
      as="font"
      type="font/otf"
      crossorigin
    />

    <link href="/src/output.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="/src/js/app.js" defer type="text/javascript"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    {% include "components/base/header.njk" %}

    <main
      class="max-w-[1280px] md:max-w-[2500px] w-full mx-auto px-2 md:px-7 py-4"
    >
      <div class="hero-section w-full flex items-center flex-col">
        <div
          class="w-full flex items-center rounded-2xl md:rounded-4xl justify-start bg-gradient-to-b from-[#EEF4FF] to-white flex-col"
        >
          <span class="text-[12px] md:text-[16px] text-primary mt-5 lg:mt-21"
            >PRIVACY POLICY</span
          >
          <h1
            class="font-jakarta text-[30px] md:text-[74px] text-[#020C22] max-w-[891px] text-center leading-tight mt-2"
          >
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-[800px] w-full mt-5 lg:mt-20 px-2">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <section>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  Craftal Web Designs ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-[24px] lg:text-[32px] text-[#020C22] font-jakarta font-semibold mb-4">
                  Information We Collect
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  We may collect non-personal information automatically through analytics tools (such as Google Analytics), including pages visited, time spent on our site, and browser/device details. We do not collect personally identifiable information unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., by contacting us).
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-[24px] lg:text-[32px] text-[#020C22] font-jakarta font-semibold mb-4">
                  How We Use Information
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  We use analytics data to improve our website, understand visitor behavior, and enhance our services.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-[24px] lg:text-[32px] text-[#020C22] font-jakarta font-semibold mb-4">
                  Cookies
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  Our site may use cookies to track usage and performance. You can disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-[24px] lg:text-[32px] text-[#020C22] font-jakarta font-semibold mb-4">
                  Data Sharing
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except when required by law.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-[24px] lg:text-[32px] text-[#020C22] font-jakarta font-semibold mb-4">
                  Your Rights
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  You may request access to or deletion of any personal information you have provided to us by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@craftal.agency" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@craftal.agency</a>.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-[24px] lg:text-[32px] text-[#020C22] font-jakarta font-semibold mb-4">
                  Contact Us
                </h2>
                <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                  If you have questions about this policy, please contact:
                </p>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <p class="text-[14px] lg:text-[18px] text-[#515A6E] leading-relaxed">
                    <strong>Craftal Web Designs</strong><br>
                    Email: <a href="mailto:info@craftal.agency" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@craftal.agency</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {% include "components/base/footer.njk" %}
  </body>
</html>
